      "comment": "REMEMBRANCE TIME (6) scored by 14 metres at Geelong over 2100m last start at her first career run. That latest effort is good enough to win a race of this calibre. WHISKEY DAWN (7) scored by 4.5 metres at this track over 2080m last start at her first career run. Must overcome a very wide draw. Meets a comparable field so she is capable of getting the job done again. MEVIA (3) finished 12th last start in a Group One over 2240m at Melton, beaten 360 metres by Adelaide Red. Should enjoy a lovely run and poses a serious threat. KITTY CASH (8) was unplaced two starts ago then things went wrong last start when she broke and finished 20 metres away in fifth over 2080m at this track. Will enjoy a pretty soft run from this draw, with the sprint lane to play a big role. Live chance in a similar assignment.",
